<problem id="fs-idm253555440">
<para id="fs-idm253555184">Which of the following elements is most likely to be used to prepare La by the reduction of La<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>: Al, C, or Fe? Why?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm151604256">
<para id="fs-idm151604000">Al is used because it is the strongest reducing agent and the only option listed that can provide sufficient driving force to convert La(III) into La.</para>
</solution>
