<para id="fs-idm108346464">(c) FeSO<sub>4</sub> is added to an acidic solution of KMnO<sub>4</sub>.</para>
<para id="fs-idm264117104">(d) Fe is added to a dilute solution of H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>.</para>
<para id="fs-idm150264128">(e) A solution of Fe(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub> and HNO<sub>3</sub> is allowed to stand in air.</para>
<para id="fs-idm272186960">(f) FeCO<sub>3</sub> is added to a solution of HClO<sub>4</sub>.</para>
<para id="fs-idm194491520">(g) Fe is heated in air.</para>
</problem>
